0teammates%20were%20fined%2025%20percent%20of%20their%20match%20fees.%20%26quot%3BRishabh%C2%A0Pant%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20captain%2C%20has%20been%20fined%20after%20his%20team%20maintained%20a%20slow%20over%20rate%20during%20their%20TATA%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20match%20against%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders...%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20IPL%20in%20a%20statement%20titled%20'IPL%20Media%20Advisory%3A%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20Breach'..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20it%20was%20his%20team's%20second%20offence%20of%20the%20season%20under%20the%20IPL's%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20relating%20to%20minimum%20over%20rate%20offences%2C%C2%A0Pant%C2%A0was%20fined%20INR%2024%20lakhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rest%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Playing%20XI%2C%20including%20the%20Impact%20Player%2C%20were%20each%20individually%20fined%20either%20INR%206%20lakhs%20or%2025%20percent%20of%20their%20respective%20match%20fees%2C%20whichever%20is%20lesser%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Capitals%20lost%20the%20game%20to%20KKR%20by%20106%20runs%20after%20the%20latter%20smashed%20272%20for%20seven%2C%20the%20second%20highest%20total%20in%20IPL%20history.%20It%20was%20Delhi%20Capitals'%20third%20loss%20in%20four%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IPL%20rules%2C%20in%20case%20of%20a%20third%20slow%20over-rate%20offense%20by%20a%20team%20in%20one%20season%2C%20the%20captain%20is%20fined%20INR%2030%20lakh%20and%20is%20handed%20over%20a%20match%20ban.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20team%20is%20imposed%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20INR%2012%20lakh%20or%2050%25%20of%20their%20match%20fee%2C%20whichever%20is%20lesser.%20So%20Pant%20needs%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20offense%20is%20not%20repeated%20by%20his%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20Star%20Sports%2C%20former%20Australia%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Michael%20Clarke%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F521-micha