3EThis%20seems%20to%20be%20for%20users%20who%20have%20over%202%2C500%20paid%20verified%20followers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20does%20it%20seem%20uncool%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWednesday%20night%2C%20something%20odd%20happened%20to%20me%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdid-elon-musk-buy-twitter-acquisition-details%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%2FX.%20An%20alert%20popped%20up%20in%20my%20notifications%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20an%20influential%20member%20of%20the%20community%20on%20X%2C%20we've%20given%20you%20a%20complimentary%20subscription%20to%20X%20Premium%20%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20blue%20checkmark%20next%20to%20my%20user%20name%20that%20had%20disappeared%20a%20year%20ago%20was%20back.%20Uh%20oh.%20I%20found%20myself%20in%20a%20tough%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20about%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-x-now-offering-cheaper-business-verification-gold-checkmark-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eold%20blue%20check%20verification%20system%20was%20dismantled%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20new%20paid%20system.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20the%20blue%20check%20has%20come%20to%20mean%20something%20very%20specific%3A%20someone%20who%20actually%20pays%20for%20X.%20Someone%20who%20is%20willing%20to%20pay%20to%20promote%20their%20own%20tweets.%20Someone%20who%20believes%20that%20X%20is%20a%20platform%20worth%20investing%20in%20rather%20than%20one%20that%20is%20slowly%20descending%20into%20chaos%20and%20irrelevance.%20Someone%20incentivized%20by%20ad-sharing%20payouts%20to%20post%20engagementbait%20and%20ragebait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(OK%2C%20I'm%20sure%20that%20not%20ALL%20people%20who%20were%20paying%20for%20a%20blue%20check%20fall%20into%20those%20categories.%20I'm%20sure%20some%20are%20just%20nice%20people%20who%20like%20the%20service.%20I%20haven't%20personally%20come%20across%20those%20people%2C%20but%20surely%20they%20exist%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20hasn't%20been%20an%20official%20explanation%20of%20why%20a%20bunch%20of%20formerly%20verified%20people%20just%20got%20a%20free%20blue%20check.%20But%20recently%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-having-terrible-year-tesla-lawsuits-compensation-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20%3C%2Fa%3Etweeted%20that%20X%20would%20be%20giving%20free%20premium%20subscriptions%20to%20users%20with%202%2C500%20paid%20subscriber%20followers.%20(X%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20clarification%20on%20this%20policy.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20affects%20people%20with%20massive%20followings%2C%20or%2C%20for%20people%20like%20me%20with%20under%20100%2C000%20followers%2C%20it%20probably%20means%20you%20have%20a%20higher-than-normal%20amount%20of%20appeal%20to%20people%20who%20pay%20for%20X.%20(In%20my%20case%2C%20I%20suspect%20it's%20because%20I've%20reported%20on%20NFTs%20and%20crypto%2C%20a%20topic%20that%20tends%20to%20attract%20paid%20blue%20checks.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20what%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20want%20people%20to%20think%20I%20%3Cem%3Epaid%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20this%20(ew).%20I%20can%20use%20the%20option%20to%20hide%20the%20blue%20check%20on%20my%20profile%20(although%20I'll%20still%20show%20up%20as%20a%20verified%20user%20in%20people's%20notification%20tab%3B%20it's%20not%20completely%20secret).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20do%20I%20keep%20the%20blue%20check%20because%20now%20there%20are%20enough%20other%20people%20who%20%3Cem%3Edon't%3C%2Fem%3E%20pay%20for%20it%20that%20it%20isn't%20an%20instant%20flag%20that%20I'm%20a%20massive%20jerk%3F%20Maybe%20it%20actually%20does%20look%20like%20I'm%20important%20and%20influential%20(and%20of%20course%2C%20I%20like%20to%20seem%20important%20and%20influential%3B%20what%20else%20do%20I%20have%20going%20for%20me%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202022%20when%20Twitter%20Blue%20first%20launched%20(pre-Elon)%2C%20I%20happily%20paid%20the%20%242.99%20a%20month%20for%20the%20extra%20features%20it%20offered.%20I%20figured%20the%20modest%20fee%20was%20worth%20it%20for%20improved%20features%20on%20an%20app%20I%20used%2C%20uh%2C%20constantly.%20And%20honestly%3F%20It%20was%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20%26quot%3BTop%20Articles%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20which%20showed%20a%20list%20of%20the%20most%20shared%20news%20stories%20among%20the%20people%20I%20followed%E2%80%94it%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20quickly%20see%20what%20stories%20people%20were%20buzzing%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20appreciated%20having%20an%20%26quot%3BUndo%26quot%3B%20button%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20after%20I%20sent%20a%20tweet%20%E2%80%94%20a%20chance%20to%20catch%20a%20typo%20or%20think%20twice%20about%20posting%20something.%20Getting%20those%20two%20features%20back%20has%20been%20wonderful%20%E2%80%94%20I%20truly%20missed%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20there's%20a%20bonus%3A%20I%20can%20rearrange%20the%20navigation%20buttons%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20app%20to%20finally%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-grok-elon-musk-ai-chatbot-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrok%3C%2Fa%3E%20tab!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20only%20reasonable%20answer%20here%20is%20to%20hide%20the%20blue%20check%20and%20enjoy%20the%20free%20features.%20Thanks%2C%20Elon%2C%20for%20the%20freebie%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20seem%20like%20a%20huckster%20creep!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-verification-blue-check-return-why-x-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712258697000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66