%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELevi%20Strauss%20CEO%20Chip%20Bergh%2C%20right%2C%20is%20joined%20by%20CFO%20Harmit%20Singh%2C%20second%20from%20right%2C%20as%20he%20rings%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20opening%20bell%2C%20Thursday%2C%20March%2021%2C%202019.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FRichard%20Drew%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELevi%20Strauss%20stock%20soared%20as%20much%20as%2020%25%20on%20Thursday%20after%20the%20company%20reported%20strong%201st%20quarter%20earnings.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BDenim%20is%20having%20a%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Levi%20Strauss%20CEO%20Michelle%20Gass%20said%20on%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELevi's%20success%20comes%20amid%20a%20new%20song%20release%20from%20Beyonce%20called%20%26quot%3BLevii's%20Jeans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Flevi-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%3ELevi%20Strauss%3C%2Fa%3E%20stock%20surged%20as%20much%20as%2020%25%20on%20Thursday%20after%20the%20company%20reported%20solid%20first%20quarter%20earnings%20results%20and%20enjoys%20added%20exposure%20thanks%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyonce-cowboy-carter-credits-producers-songwriters-2024-4%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20song%20from%20Beyonc%C3%A9.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20jeans%20maker%20said%20sales%20fell%20about%208%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20recent%20cost-cutting%20measures%20helped%20drive%20a%20better%20than%20expected%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20were%20the%20key%20numbers%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevenue%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%241.56%20billion%2C%20versus%20analyst%20estimates%20of%20%241.55%20billion%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjusted%20earnings%20per%20share%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%240.26%2C%20versus%20analyst%20esti