r%20a%20second%20time.%20The%20SP%20first%20chose%20Bhanu%20Pratap%20Singh%20to%20contest%20a%20seat%20that%20has%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20since%202004%20but%20protests%20by%20the%20party's%20local%20cadre%20prompted%20a%20change.%20In%20came%20Atul%20Pradhan%20-%20the%20Sardhana%20MLA%20-%20but%20his%20ticket%20was%20swiftly%20passed%20to%20Sunita%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Verma%20-%20who%20was%20expelled%20from%20rivals%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20in%202019%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20two-time%20MLA%20Yogesh%20Verma%20-%20filed%20her%20nomination%20papers%20Thursday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%20Atul%20Pradhan%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20brining%20the%20Vermas%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20relations%20soured%20after%20the%202022%20Assembly%20election%2C%20in%20which%20Mr%20Pradhan%20won%20from%20Sardhana%20and%20Mr%20Verma%20lost%20the%20Hastinapur%20seat.%20Sources%20have%20said%20the%20Vermas%20believe%20Mr%20Pradhan%20did%20not%20extend%20the%20desired%20help%20in%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pradhan%20-%20whose%20brief%20tenure%20as%20the%20Meerut%20candidate%20drew%20jibes%20from%20RLD%20boss%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20-%20has%20toed%20the%20party%20line%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhomever%20the%20party%20chooses%2C%20I%20will%20support%20their%20nomination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeerut-lok-sabha-election-2024-news-samajwadi-party-jayant-chaudharys-lucky-few-jibe-at-samajwadi-partys-candidate-swaps-5372479%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BLucky%20Few%26quot%3B%3A%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20Mocks%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Flip-Flop%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplacing%20candidates%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20an%20election%20isn't%20uncommon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%20it%20may%20be%20because%20the%20party%20has%20reassessed%20its%20chances%20of%20winning%20a%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20Meerut%20change%20was%20for%20many%20reasons%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20because%20Mrs%20Verma%20is%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%20and%20the%20city%20is%20home%20to%20over%20four%20lakh%20Dalits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Mayor%20of%20Meerut%2C%20Mrs%20Verma%20will%20take%20on%20one%20of%20the%20BJP's%20newer%20recruits%20-%20actor%20Arun%20Govil%2C%20who%20played%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%20popular%20Ramayan%20series%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20multiple%20changes%2C%20for%20the%20same%20seat%2C%20are%20uncommon%20and%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20signs%20a%20party%20is%20struggling%20to%20match%20potentially%20winning%20candidates%20with%20just%20the%20right%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Meerut%2C%20the%20SP%20has%20run%20into%20difficulties%20in%20Moradabad%2C%20Rampur%2C%20and%20Budaun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Moradabad%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20initially%20nominated%20ST%20Hassan%2C%20but%20later%20Ruchi%20Veera's%20name%20came%20up.%20There%20were%20protests%20by%20local%20cadre.%20Confusion%20prevailed%20as%20both%20filed%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%20Ruchi%20Veera's%20candidature%20was%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20in%20Rampur%20-%20the%20bastion%20of%20Azam%20Khan%2C%20where%20the%20jailed%20leader%20still%20has%20immense%20sway%20-%20there%20was%20a%20brief%20face-off%20between%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20pick%20and%20that%20of%20Asim%20Raja%20from%20Azam%20Khan's%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Mr%20Yadav's%20candidate%2C%20Asim%20Raza%2C%20filed%20the%20nomination%2C%20but%20this%20was%20settled%20only%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20penultimate%20day%20of%20filing%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20chaos%20prevailed%20in%20Budaun%2C%20where%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20cousin%2C%20Dharmendra%2C%20was%20given%20the%20ticket%20that%20was%20first%20also%20wanted%20by%20his%20uncle%2C%20Shivpal%20Yadav%2C%20before%20he%20demanded%20it%20for%20his%20son%2C%20Aditya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-who-is-dharmendra-yadav-samajwadi-partys-azamgarh-candidate-5269139%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWho%20Is%20Dharmendra%20Yadav%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Azamgarh%20Pick%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budaun%20dilemma%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20settled.%20Technically%20the%20candidature%20is%20held%20by%20Shivpal%20Yadav%2C%20but%20sources%20indicate%20it%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20settled%20in%20favour%20of%20his%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20Mr%20Yadav's%20party%20has%20also%20changed%20out%20candidates%20for%20the%20Baghpat%2C%20Bijnor%2C%20Gautam%20Buddh%20Nagar%2C%20Misrikh%2C%20and%20Sambal%20seats%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20Khajuraho%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20Sambal%20-%20a%20seat%20the%20SP%20won%20in%202019%20-%20was%20necessitated%20because%20the%20MP%2C%20Shafiqur%20Rahman%20Barq%2C%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2093.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20contesting%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20UP's%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20-%20it%20received%2063%20as%20part%20of%20its%20deal%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20will%20contest%2017%2C%20including%20its%20family%20bastions%20of%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli.%20UP%20will%20vote%20in%20each%20of%20the%20seven%20phases%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712245140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F19rtlt1g_akhilesh-yadav-1200_625x300_19_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originI