arian%20Thali%20To%20Cost%207%25%20More%20As%20Onion%2C%20Tomato%20Prices%20Soar%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20became%20dearer%20by%207%20per%20cent%20in%20March%20primarily%20due%20to%20the%20rise%20in%20onion%2C%20tomato%2C%20and%20potato%20prices%2C%20an%20arm%20of%20domestic%20rating%20agency%20Crisil%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cool%20down%20in%20poultry%20prices%20led%20to%20a%207%20per%20cent%20decline%20in%20non-vegetarian%20thali%2C%20Crisil%20Market%20Intelligence%20and%20Analysis%20said%20in%20its%20monthly%20%26quot%3BRoti%20Rice%20Rate%26quot%3B%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20a%20vegetable%20thali%20--%20comprising%20roti%2C%20vegetables%20(onions%2C%20tomatoes%20and%20potatoes)%2C%20rice%2C%20dal%2C%20curd%20and%20salad%20--%20increased%20to%20Rs%2027.3%20per%20plate%20in%20March%20from%20Rs%2025.5%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period%2C%20but%20was%20cheaper%20than%20Rs%2027.4%20in%20February%202024%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20the%20veg%20thali%20increased%20due%20to%20a%20surge%20of%2040%20per%20cent%2C%2036%20per%20cent%20and%2022%20per%20cent%20on-year%20in%20prices%20of%20onion%2C%20tomato%20and%20potato%2C%20respectively%2C%20due%20to%20lower%20arrivals%20of%20onion%20and%20potato%20and%20low%20base%20of%20last%20fiscal%20for%20tomatoes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20noted%20that%20due%20to%20lower%20arrivals%2C%20prices%20of%20rice%20increased%2014%20per%20cent%20and%20pulses%20by%2022%20per%20cent%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20year-ago%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20non-veg%20thali%2C%20in%20which%20only%20dal%20gets%20replaced%20by%20chicken%2C%20the%20price%20declined%20to%20Rs%2054.9%20as%20against%20Rs%2059.2%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period%2C%20but%20was%20higher%20when%20compared%20with%20Rs%2054%20per%20thali%20in%20preceding%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2016%20per%20cent%20decline%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20broiler%20prices%2C%20which%20has%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20weight%20in%20the%20overall%20price%2C%20was%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20cost%20of%20non-vegetarian%20thali%20on%20a%20year-on-year%20basis%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20compared%20with%20February%2C%20the%20prices%20of%20broiler%20increased%205%20per%20cent%20because%20of%20the%20start%20of%20the%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan%20and%20higher%20demand%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712239800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fl9mmhl08_tomatoes-generic-afp_625x300_28_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvegetarian-thali-to-cost-7-more-as-onion-tomato-prices-soar-report-5373407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cost%20of%20a%20vegetarian%20thali%20became%20dearer%20by%207%20per%20cent%20in%20March%20primarily%20due%20to%20the%20rise%20in%20onion%2C%20tomato%2C%20and%20potato%20prices%2C%20an%20arm%20of%20domestic%20rating%20agency%20Crisil%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvegetarian-thali-to-cost-7-more-as-onion-tomato-prices-soar-report-5373407%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvegetarian-thali-to-cost-7-more-as-onion-tomato-prices-soar-report-5373407%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvegetarian-thali-to-cost-7-more-as-onion-tomato-prices-soar-report-5373407%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20applications%20for%20jobless%20benefits%20rise%20to%20highest%20level%20in%20two%20months%2C%20but%2