%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20further%20points%20out%20that%2C%20unlike%20heirloom%20varieties%2C%20the%20seed%20saved%20from%20hybrids%20does%20not%20grow%20true%20to%20its%20type%20in%20the%20next%20cycle.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20be%20less%20vigorous%20and%20more%20genetically%20variable.%20If%20you%20cannot%20replicate%20it%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20keeping%20the%20seeds.%20It%20only%20compels%20farmers%20to%20buy%20new%20seeds%20every%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%20As%20they%20are%20open-pollinated%2C%20you%20can%20easily%20replicate%20those%20seeds%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20produce%20harvested%20from%20both%20varieties%20differ%2C%20Neelam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20tomatoes%20are%20available%20year-round%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20past%20when%20we%20only%20had%20them%20in%20winter.%20To%20satisfy%20demand%2C%20farmers%20now%20grow%20tomatoes%20in%20mountainous%20areas%20with%20heavy%20fertiliser%20use.%20However%2C%20organically%20grown%20tomatoes%20in%20their%20respective%20seasons%20may%20not%20last%20as%20long%20but%20are%20richer%20in%20nutrients%2C%20tastier%2C%20and%20more%20vibrant%20in%20colour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20France%2C%20various%20tomato%20varieties%20were%20once%20used%20in%20different%20recipes%2C%20but%20now%20a%20single%2C%20sweeter%20tomato%20is%20used%20universally%2C%20replacing%20the%20sour%20ones%20of%20the%20past.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neelam%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346321%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeelam%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20point%20doing%20all%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20work%20received%20a%20great%20response%20from%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20going%20beyond%20conserving%20seeds%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%20Neelam%20now%20trains%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20in%20seed%20conservation.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast%20%E2%80%94%20including%20states%20like%20Nagaland%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20them%20grow%20and%20conserve%20their%20own%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20Neelam%20sells%20approximately%208%2C000%20packets%20of%20heirloom%20seeds%20at%20Rs%2099%20each%20to%20farmers.%20With%20these%20seeds%20and%20the%20training%20he%20provides%2C%20farmers%20can%20cultivate%20crops%20and%20harvest%20new%20seeds%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%20ensuring%20sustainable%20food%20security%20%E2%80%94%20a%20goal%20Neelam%20passionately%20pursues%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20Diganata%20Bora%20has%20been%20cultivating%20vegetables%20using%20such%20heirloom%20seeds%20on%20his%20two-acre%20farm%20in%20Paschim%20Manjiri%20village%20of%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20hybrid%20varieties%2C%20we%20get%20good%20yield%20using%20heirloom%20ones.%20In%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B0.33%20acre%5D%2C%20we%20now%20get%206-7%20quintals%20of%20vegetables%20over%202-2.5%20quintals.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20input%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%20as%20we%20use%20readily%20available%20cow%20dung%20as%20fertiliser.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20switch%3B%20now%20our%20soil%20fertility%20has%20also%20improved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Diganata%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20concludes%2C%20%E2%80%9CBack%20when%20I%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20no%20resources%20available%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20from.%20Now%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20to%20have%20created%20a%20helpful%20platform%20for%20other%20farmers.%20When%20I%20visit%20their%20fields%2C%20I%20feel%20great%20to%20see%20the%20joy%20on%20their%20faces.%20By%20cultivating%20their%20own%20organic%20seeds%20and%20crops%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20made%20agriculture%20economically%20viable%20in%20our%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Neelam%20Dutta.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712239080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alarmed%20by%20the%20effect%20of%20climate%20change%20on%20food%20security%2C%20Assam-based%20Neelam%20Dutta%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20safeguard%20heirloom%20seeds.%20Under%20his%20venture%20%E2%80%98Pabhoi%20Greens%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%2024%2C000%20farmers%20in%20Northeast%20India%20in%20organic%20cultivation%20and%20seed%20preservation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346317%2Fassam-organic-farmer-neelam-dutta-conserves-climate-resilient-heirloom-seeds-pabhoi-greens-northeast%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CAA%20A%20%26quot%3BTrap%26quot%3B%20Or%20Is%20It%20%26quot%3BRumour%20And%20Lies%26quot%3B%3F%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Vs%20PM%20In%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECooch%20Behar%2C%20the%20crucial%20north%20Bengal%20district%2C%20became%20subject%20to%20strong%20opposing%20political%20views%20today%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20rallies%20within%2030%20km%20of%20each%20other.%20While%20Ms%20Banerjee%20labelled%20the%20BJP%20worse%20than%20a%20snake%20--%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20trust%20a%20snake%20and%20even%20pet%20it%2C%20but%20not%20the%20BJP%26quot%3B%20---%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20addressed%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20the%20burning%20political%20issue%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act.%20But%20his%20defence%20was%20crouched%20in%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20--%20the%20CAA%20is%20being%20tarred%20to%20remove%20attention%20from%20corruption%2C%20he%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Ms%20Banerjee%20or%20her%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(INDIA%20bloc)%20never%20cared%20for%20the%20marginalised%20communities.%20Now%20that%20we%20have%20brought%20CAA%2C%20they%20are%20spreading%20rumours%20and%20lies.%20It%20is%20Modi%20ki%20guarantee%20to%20provide%20citizenship%20to%20those%20who%20have%20faith%20in%20Maa%20Bharati%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20this%20evening%2C%20addressing%20a%20rally%20at%20the%20Rash%20Mela%20grounds%20in%20Cooch%20Behar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20saying%20remove%20corruption%3B%20the%20opposition%20is%20saying%20'save%20the%20corrupt.'%20I%20will%20ensure%20the%20corrupt%20are%20punished%2C%20and%20the%20poor%20get%20justice.%20In%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20more%20stringent%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20corrupt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20reference%20to%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20which%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20hot%20button%20issue%20in%20this%20election.%C2%A0%20While%20Trinamool%20was%20trying%20to%20save%20the%20culprits%20of%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20BJP's%20focus%20is%20empowering%20the%20women.%20The%20culprits%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20will%20spend%20their%20lives%20in%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20issue%20was%20addressed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Cooch%20Behar%20around%20noon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20one%20registers%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20one%20will%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20from%20Bangladesh%20and%20they%20will%20lose%20all%20basic%20rights%2C%20she%20told%20her%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20you%20submit%20your%20name%20for%20registration%2C%20you%20will%20be%20declared%20a%20Bangladeshi.%20This%20means%20you%20will%20not%20get%20the%20benefits%20under%20Lakhishree%2C%20Kanyashee%2C%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20vote%2C%20you%20will%20not%20have%20citizenship%20rights%2C%20government%20rights.%20Think%20yourself%20whether%20it%20is%20good%20or%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CAA%20is%20a%20trap%20to%20turn%20legal%20citizens%20into%20foreigners.%20Once%20you%20(BJP)%20implement%20CAA%2C%20NRC%20will%20follow...%20Remember%20CAA%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20fish%2C%20the%20tail%20is%20the%20NRC%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20snake%20analogy%20to%20claim%20the%20BJp%20is%20not%20to%20be%20trusted..%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20allow%20neither%20CAA%20nor%20NRC%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20If%20you%20apply%2C%20you%20will%20be%20designated%20as%20foreigners%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20win%2025%20of%20the%20state's%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20coming%20election%2C%20a%20chunk%20of%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20from%20north%20Bengal%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20consolidated%20its%20base%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20re-nominated%20the%20sitting%20MP%2C%20junior%20home%20minister%20Nisith%20Pramanik%2C%20from%20Cooch%20Behar.%C2%A0%20The%20Trinamool%20has%20fielded%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20of%20Sitai%2C%20Rajbanshi%20community%20member%20Jagadish%20Barma%20Basunia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20claimed%20today%20that%20the%20minister%20is%20a%20Trinamool%20reject.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20national%20shame%20that%20a%20person%20against%20whom%20there%20are%20several%20cases%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs.%20He%20was%20sacked%20from%20our%20party.%20Now%2C%20he%20is%20the%20asset%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pramanik%2C%20a%20former%20leader%20of%20the%20Trinamool's%20youth%20wing%2C%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20party%20in%202018%2C%20after%20which%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712238180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F2m4rhch8_mamata-banerjee_625x300_31_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-in-focus-as-pm-modi-mamata-banerjee-court-north-bengal-537443