3107822%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20'Shri'%20To%20Be%20Prefixed%20Before%20Names%20Of%20Defence%20Officers%3A%20RTI%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20instances%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20where%20Shri%20was%20being%20used%20before%20names%20of%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20officers%20instead%20of%20their%20ranks%2C%20the%20President's%20Secretariat%20in%20an%20RTI%20reply%20has%20explained%20that%20only%20ranks%20have%20to%20be%20used%20before%20names%20of%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20and%20defence%20officers%20in%20official%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremonial%20section%20of%20the%20President's%20Secretariat%20in%20May%202023%20issued%20a%20letter%20that%20stated%20that%20for%20both%20serving%20and%20retired%20officials%2C%20only%20their%20ranks%20have%20to%20be%20prefixed%20before%20their%20names%20and%20Shri%20was%20not%20to%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20RTI%20application%20filed%20by%20an%20individual%2C%20the%20President's%20Secretariat%20confirmed%20that%20the%20order%20in%20this%20regard%20was%20applicable%20to%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20officials%20also%2C%20the%20RTI%20reply%20accessed%20by%20ANI%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20officials%20said%20that%20this%20is%20a%20step%20towards%20upholding%20protocol%20for%20the%20usage%20of%20titles%20for%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20Officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20developments%2C%20a%20number%20of%20instances%20were%20coming%20where%20incorrect%20usage%20of%20titles%20for%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20(ICG)%20officers%20in%20various%20communications%20were%20noticed.%20This%20discrepancy%20is%20contrary%20to%20established%20service%20traditions%2C%20and%20notified%20government%20directives%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20usage%20of%20correct%20ranks%20in%20official%20communications%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20matter%20of%20formality%3B%20it%20is%20also%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20our%20service%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20practice%20plays%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20maintaining%20mutual%20respect%20between%20services%2C%20fostering%20a%20professional%20environment%2C%20and%20upholding%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20officials%20have%20foreseen%20hope%20that%20the%20discrepancy%20would%20be%20promptly%20rectified%20by%20all%20services%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20correct%20ranks%20of%20ICG%20officers%20are%20appropriately%20acknowledged%20in%20all%20official%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20of%20India%20is%20the%20supreme%20commander%20of%20the%20defence%20forces%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%2C%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%20along%20with%20the%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20are%20the%20four%20forces%20under%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20and%20are%20governed%20by%20their%20different%20acts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712237820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Feauqs774_indian-armed-forces-flags-ndtv-file-photo_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-shri-to-be-prefixed-before-names-of-coast-guard-defence-officers-rti-reply-5373743%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20instances%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20where%20Shri%20was%20being%20used%20before%20names%20of%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20officers%20instead%20of%20their%20ranks%2C%20an%20RTI%20reply%20has%20explained%20that%20only%20ranks%20have%20to%20be%20used%20before%20names%20of%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20and%20defence%20officers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-shri-to-be-prefixed-before-names-of-coast-guard-defence-officers-rti-reply-5373743%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-shri-to-be-prefixed-before-names-of-coast-guard-defence-officers-rti-reply-5373743%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-shri-to-be-prefixed-before-names-of-coast-guard-defence-officers-rti-reply-5373743%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20Tesla%20Begins%20Making%20Cars%20In%20Germany%20For%20Export%20To%20India%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20begun%20production%20of%20right-hand%20drive%20cars%20at%20its%20plant%20in%20Germany%20for%20export%20to%20India%20later%20this%20year%2C%20three%20people%20aware%20of%20the%20company's%20plans%20told%20Reuters%2C%20as%20it%20moves%20ahead%20with%20a%20possible%20entry%20into%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20car%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20from%20Tesla%20is%20expected%20to%20visit%20India%20later%20this%20month%20to%20look%20at%20sites%20for%20a%20local%20car%20manufacturing%20plant%20that%20would%20require%20an%20investment%20of%20about%20%242%20billion%2C%20said%20two%20of%20the%20three%20people%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20be%20named%20because%20the%20plans%20are%20not%20public%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20last%20month%20slashed%20the%20import%20tax%20rate%20on%20certain%20electric%20vehicles%20if%20their%20makers%20invest%20at%20least%20%24500%20million%20in%20the%20country%20and%20start%20production%20there%20within%20three%20years.%20The%20move%20is%20a%20win%20for%20Tesla%2C%20which%20had%20lobbied%20for%20months%20for%20lower%20taxes%2C%20but%20faced%20resistance%20from%20local%20carmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right-hand%20drive%20cars%20which%20will%20be%20allocated%20to%20India%2C%20they%20have%20started%20building%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said%2C%20with%20some%20cars%20due%20to%20be%20shipped%20to%20India%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-tesla-to-explore-locations-in-india-for-3-billion-ev-factory-report-5374671%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20To%20Explore%20Locations%20In%20India%20For%20%243%20Billion%20EV%20Factory%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20which%20model%20Tesla%20plans%20to%20export%20to%20India.%20It%20currently%20produces%20only%20the%20Model%20Y%20at%20its%20factory%20near%20Berlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20Indian%20policy%2C%20companies%20can%20import%20up%20to%208%2C000%20cars%20a%20year%20at%20the%20lower%20tax%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20an%20email%20seeking%20comment%20outside%20U.S.%20office%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plans%20for%20shipments%20to%20India%20are%20the%20first%20indication%20of%20right-hand%20drive%20(RHD)%20cars%20being%20produced%20in%20Berlin.%20Tesla's%20Shanghai%20plant%2C%20its%20primary%20export%20hub%20located%20nearer%20to%20right-hand-drive%20markets%2C%20such%20as%20Australia%20and%20Japan%2C%20has%20so%20far%20handled%20production%20of%20such%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20imported%20RHD%20Model%20Y%20vehicles%20for%20its%20launch%20in%20the%20UK%20from%20China%20and%20has%20not%20said%20whether%20it%20has%20shifted%20to%20importing%20from%20Berlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20carmaker%20has%20eyed%20the%20Indian%20market%20for%20years%20and%20its%20officials%20visited%20the%20country%20several%20times%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20also%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20New%20York%20last%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla's%20push%20into%20India%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20slowing%20EV%20demand%20in%20its%20main%20U.S.%20and%20China%20markets%20coincides%20with%20intensifying%20competition%20from%20Chinese%20players.%20That%20caused%20Tesla%20to%20report%20a%20drop%20in%20its%20first-quarter%20deliveries%20and%20miss%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla's%20India%20entry%20plan%20also%20includes%20investment%20in%20a%20charging%20network%2C%20which%20will%20come%20on%20top%20of%20the%20%242%20billion%20earmarked%20for%20the%20plant%2C%20and%20sourcing%20more%20components%20locally%2C%20said%20one%20of%20the%20three%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla%20already%20imports%20parts%20from%20India%20and%20is%20now%20looking%20at%20reducing%20sourcing%20from%20China%20and%20making%20India%20a%20bigger%20sourcing%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Maharashtra%20in%20the%20west%2C%20and%20Modi's%20home%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20for%20its%20factory%2C%20which%20it%20expects%20to%20build%20in%20two%20years%2C%20two%20of%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20EV%20market%2C%20small%20but%20growing%2C%20is%20dominated%20by%20domestic%20carmaker%20Tata%20Motors.%20Electric%20models%20made%20up%202%25%20of%20total%20car%20sales%20in%202023%20but%20the%20government%20is%20targeting%2030%25%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Tesla's%20Vietnamese%20rival%20VinFast%20agreed%20to%20invest%20%242%20billion%20in%20India%20and%20started%20building%20an%20EV%20factory%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712237340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fro3eqek_tesla_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-tesla-begins-making-cars-in-germany-for-export-to-india-report-5374713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20has%20begun%20production%20of%20right-hand%20drive%20cars%20at%20its%20plant%20in%20Germany%20for%20export%20to%20India%20later%20thi