et%20bat!%E2%80%9D%20Forthcoming%20about%20his%20passion%20for%20sports%2C%20Bakhtyar%2C%20who%20is%20now%20Managing%20Director%20at%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%2C%20had%20another%20favourite%20pastime%20too%20%E2%80%94%20watching%20the%20butter%20churner%20and%20the%20old-fashioned%20pasteuriser%20at%20the%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20old%20machinery%2C%20Bakhtyar%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343315%2Fbiggest-millet-exporters-in-india-ra-foods-sisters-priya-akila-gunasekar-run-multi-crore-millet-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%20still%20houses%20some%20of%20the%20ancient%20horse%20carts%20and%20carriages%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Gerber%20that%20was%20once%20used%20to%20test%20milk%20and%20an%20old%20weighing%20scale%20that%20stood%20right%20behind%20the%20main%20entrance%20of%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Parvana%20shares%20their%20love%20for%20the%20last%20antique%20(%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20tiny%20and%20the%20scale%20was%20six%20times%20our%20size.%20We%20have%20spent%20hours%20checking%20our%20weight%20on%20it%E2%80%9D)%2C%20all%20the%20cousins%20agree%20in%20unison.%20And%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20though%20they%20now%20head%20different%20verticals%20at%20the%20brand%2C%20they%20are%20united%20by%20these%20core%20memories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-2-1711120311.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20was%20started%20by%20Nariman%20Ardeshir%20who%20began%20selling%20milk%20cans%20to%20people%20in%20Mumbai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-2-1711120311.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t