-irani-congress-lok-sabha-election-2024-if-amethi-wants-me-robert-vadra-hints-at-contesting-lok-sabha-polls-5374375%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famethi-robert-vadra-smriti-irani-congress-lok-sabha-election-2024-if-amethi-wants-me-robert-vadra-hints-at-contesting-lok-sabha-polls-5374375%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Gourav%20Vallabh's%20Digs%20At%20Congress%2C%20An%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Reference%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDoubling%20down%20on%20his%20allegations%20against%20the%20Congress%20hours%20after%20he%20quit%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20Gourav%20Vallabh%20has%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20being%20against%20wealth%20creators%20and%20said%20its%20silence%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Babuse%26quot%3B%20of%20Sanatan%20dharma%20was%20a%20sign%20of%20its%20tacit%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Vallabh%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20his%20former%20party's%20ally%20and%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20calling%20him%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20corrupt%20person%20of%20this%20age%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20piece%20of%20clothing%20with%20the%20BJP's%20symbol%2C%20the%20lotus%2C%20emblazoned%20on%20it%2C%20the%20former%20Congress%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20wealth%20creators%20have%20to%20be%20respected%2C%20they%20create%20employment%20for%20the%20country.%20Abusing%20them%20doesn't%20help%20the%20GDP%20or%20solve%20any%20problem.%20You%20can't%20abuse%20our%20unicorns%2C%20I%20can't%20do%20that.%20The%20Congress%20is%20now%20criticising%20its%20own%20policies.%20Congress%20governments%20implemented%20liberalisation%2C%20privatisation%20and%20globalisation%20and%20now%20the%20party%20is%20making%20comments%20against%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20also%20%26quot%3Babused%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20that%20had%20bought%20Air%20India%20during%20its%20disinvestment%2C%20Mr%20Vallabh%20said%20all%20moves%20of%20the%20government%20can't%20be%20bad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20party's%20alliance%20with%20the%20AAP%2C%20Mr%20Vallabh%2C%20who%20had%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20elections%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EKalyug%20ka%20sabse%20bada%20bhrashtachari%3C%2Fem%3E%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%3Cem%3Ehai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20most%20corrupt%20person%20of%20this%20age).%20Because%20if%20a%20thief%20ends%20up%20stealing%2C%20that%20is%20expected%2C%20but%20he%20came%20to%20power%20after%20making%20tall%20claims.%20How%20can%20you%20(the%20Congress)%20support%20a%20person%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20statements%20by%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20and%20others%2C%20the%20former%20Congress%20leader%20said%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20was%20abused%20and%20Congress%20remained%20silent.%20He%20also%20alluded%20to%20the%20Congress%20refusing%20to%20attend%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20comes%20to%20your%20house%20with%20an%20(invitation)%20card%2C%20have%20you%20ever%20seen%20anyone%20giving%20in%20writing%20that%20they%20will%20not%20go%3F%20What%20is%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20his%20responsibilities%20in%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%2C%20given%20that%20he%20has%20switched%20sides%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Vallabh%20said%20he%20did%20not%20know.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20calculate%20everything.%20I%20do%20what%20my%20heart%20tells%20me%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712235660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F51aggf58_gourav-vallabh_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-gourav-vallabhs-digs-at-congress-an-arvind-kejriwal-reference-5374505%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doubling%20down%20on%