eveloped.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20foetus%20stays%20alive%20till%20the%20umbilical%20cord%20is%20intact.%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20cord%20is%20clamped%20and%20cut%2C%20it%20dies.%20Given%20the%20sensitivity%2C%20nobody%20wanted%20to%20touch%20this%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20these%20women.%20He%20got%20his%20first%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20apex%20court%20when%20he%20garnered%20the%20support%20of%20320%20women%20who%20had%20abnormal%20foetuses%2C%20were%20minor%20rape%20survivors%20and%20from%20low%20socio-economic%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-3-1711970661-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202019%2C%20Dr%20Nikhil%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20justice%20for%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nikhil%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20a%20law%20degree%2C%20burnt%20the%20midnight%20oil%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20this%20case.%20From%20drafting%2C%20coordinating%20with%20the%20right%20contacts%2C%20creating%20adequate%20evidence%2C%20and%20responding%20to%20medical%20as%20well%20as%20legal%20questions%2C%20he%20meticulously%20planned%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1705381%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%2520has%2520approved%2Con%252017th%2520March%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202021%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20amend%20the%20MTP%20Act%201971.%20The%20Bill%20was%20approved%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20enhanced%20the%20upper%20gestation%20limit%20from%2020%20to%2024%20weeks%20for%20special%20categories%20of%20women%20which%20will%20be%20defined%20in%20the%20amendments%20of%20the%20Act.%20It%20would%20include%20survivors%20of%20rape%2C%20victims%20of%20incest%2C%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20women%20such%20as%20disabled%20women%20and%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20again%20an%20arbitrary%20limit%2C%2024%20weeks%20is%20still%20a%20pretty%20decent%20time%20frame%20to%20detect%20abnormalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20his%20patients%2C%20this%20judgement%20has%20been%20extremely%20satisfying%20for%20Dr%20Nikhil%20personally%2C%20who%20has%20fought%20multiple%20challenges%20and%20threats%20in%20various%20forms%20in%20his%2014-year%20crusade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20we%20see%20families%20starting%20with%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20children.%20We%20become%20a%20part%20of%20these%20units%20as%20they%20remember%20us%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20get%2030%20such%20cases%20every%20month.%20But%20when%20you%20are%20able%20to%20contribute%20towards%20a%20larger%20policy%20change%2C%20you%20are%20able%20to%20impact%20lakhs%20and%20crores%20of%20lives%20known%20and%20unknown%20to%20you.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20whole%20new%20level%20of%20satisfaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Nikhil%20Datar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1705381%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%2520has%2520approved%2Con%252017th%2520March%25202020.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%20passes%20The%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202021%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20PIB%20Delhi%20published%20on%207%20March%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711972183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FDr-Nikhil-Datar-2-1711970423.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Nikhil%20Datar's%20efforts%20led%20to%20the%20amendment%20of%20the%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20Act%201971%2C%20sparking%20a%20much%20needed%20conversation%20about%20how%20an%20outdated%20and%20medically%20unsound%20law%20was%20harming%20women.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346145%2Ftermination-of-pregnancy-act-india-dr-nikhil-datar-case-legal-battle-to-raise-abortion-limit%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20Spent%20%243.1%20Million%20On%20Anti-Union%20Consultants%20In%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20company%E2%80%99s%20labor%20battles%20have%2