24%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20an%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Old%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20does%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20brand%20necessitate%20breaking%20away%20from%20your%20Sankethi%20roots%20on%20the%20odd%20occasion%3F%20Bharat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20agree%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAdukale%20has%20always%20been%20a%20Karnataka%20brand%3B%20our%20roots%20are%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20the%20culinary%20heritage%20of%20the%20region.%20Similar%20to%20national%20brands%2C%20our%20products%20have%20their%20own%20USP%20%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20growth%20factor%20in%20the%20markets%20we%20operate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20world%20is%20our%20platter%20and%20cross-border%20integration%20of%20food%20has%20never%20been%20better.%20People%20thrive%20on%20homegrown%20recipes%20and%20products%20that%20are%20a%20window%20to%20different%20cultures.%20Given%20this%20background%2C%20our%20core%20will%20always%20remain%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20Adukale%20in%202017%2C%20Bharat%20became%20director%20in%202019%2C%20and%20subsequently%20the%20CEO%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Adukale%20enjoys%20an%20extensive%20s