ning%20purposes%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251019%2Fwildlife-rescue-kashmir-woman-teacher-leopard-bear-aaliya-mir-math-teacher-animal-human-conflict-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleopards%E2%80%99%20habitats%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20along%20with%20a%20few%20locals%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20and%20support%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20Forest%20Department%20led%20by%20then%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest%20Officer)%20of%20Pali%20%E2%80%94%20IFS%20Balaji%20Kari%20%E2%80%94%20put%20their%20heads%20together%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20stop%20this%20from%20snowballing%20into%20a%20catastrophe.%20But%20as%20they%20would%20soon%20discover%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20spent%20the%20majority%20of%20three%20years%20having%20countless%20meetings%20with%20government%20officials%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20ministers%20where%20he%20convinced%20the%20room%20that%20Jawai%20was%20the%20natural%20habitat%20of%20leopards%2C%20and%20that%20the%20area%20housed%20tremendous%20tourism%20potential.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20Government%20gave%20a%20premature%20termination%20notice%20to%20all%20the%20mines.%20The%20activity%20was%20soon%20discontinued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%2C%20who%20had%20quit%20a%20lucrative%20job%20in%20winemaking%20to%20turn%20his%20attention%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20now%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F179096%2Fifs-officer-hero-mumbai-leopard-human-conflict-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20dream%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20envisioned%20that%20the%20land%20that%20he%20had%20fought%20so%20hard%20to%20protect%20would%20now%20be%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20the%20leopards%20and%20those%20who%20loved%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Bera%20Safari%20Lodge%20stands%20on%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20and%2